g.title: 2D-Sprechblase.1539
g.desc: This is a simple example for FSMER. The modeled factory is di...
g.text: This is a simple example for FSMER. The modeled factory is divided into its three main functional sections PS, BS and SDS. The product is produced in the PS. Therefore, different materials and energy are required from the SDS. The PS is located in the BS which requires heat energy from the SDS-BS. Furthermore, the machine 2 is described in detail by its functional model.
